Text: 'If Han and Chewie are in a battle together, add two battle destiny. OR Search your Reserve Deck, take Falcon into hand, and reshuffle. OR If Han is defending a battle alone, you may ''react'' by deploying Chewie there (for free) from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
